title: ~D5 Hardstuck ADC Main Searching for Coach
body:
Hey, since season 6 im always beeing around D5 as an Adc Main and i dont know why i just cant "Climb" or improve , i really need a coach to get me out of this slump . So im hoping to fine an Adc Main between Challenger and D1 ( or just a great Coach) that can teach me what i do wrong , what i have to look for etc. 
My ingame name is Farid Peng : http://euw.op.gg/summoner/userName=Farid%20Peng
For lessons i would although pay money. Please feel free to add me ingame or leave a Comment where i could look for one :) 
Great new Year Everyone

Languages : ENG + GER
